des:
This StoryQube Original Game is one that brings a family together to have a great time. 

Baby Momo is one of the most sweetest babies in the world, but he has one major problem. He bursts out crying whenever he listens to any sound that is foreign to him, any sound he hasn't heard before. 

The only way to make him stop crying and get back to cute giggling that fills our hearts with love, is to say Baby Momo, please don't cry, It is just Thunder, or It is just a car, or It is just a cat depending on what new sound he just heard. 

So identify the sounds and make sure Baby Momo stops crying!
